{"tid":778913,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人用過S_nMarket集運","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T22:05:14.000Z","uid":42457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b15243636825e14dfd5876289f4597080131b2","tid":778913,"uid":42457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"其實呢間公司既集運除咗可以運危險品之外<br />\n一啲優勝之處都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奉勸大家如非必要都唔好用佢地<br />\n<br />\n又慢又唔係平過人，<br />\n如果集運完想寄去智能櫃<br />\n仲要去過數再影入數紙比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱好似一星期先會寄一次智能櫃既貨品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔係佢地所講既簡單方便快捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n差唔多價位可以用bns/shxpbao<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"> 利申：非打手，買香水集運已中伏</span></span>"},{"pid":"78a63ff1c0172aae08bc1e93b4cb9e42479726f3","tid":778913,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過，一般淘寶用易兔， 美國/日本用bns"},{"pid":"6499fd51efab362e9d2cd49b12bcc27efd8934ec","tid":778913,"uid":124741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"呢間好鳩耐啦<br />\n即係以前咩SUNNY代購<br />\n比高登仔屌到仆街<br />\n我都中過伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0e9136fc075d8fb3263f6f587659d42609c325","tid":778913,"uid":42457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6499fd51efab362e9d2cd49b12bcc27efd8934ec","tid":778913,"uid":124741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"呢間好鳩耐啦<br />\n即係以前咩SUNNY代購<br />\n比高登仔屌到仆街<br />\n我都中過伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.